data.description: This super charming house located in the heart of Aurelia won't last long!  This home has a nice sun porch, a breezeway to the attached garage along with a detached garage all situated on a large corner lot.  Recent updates include new flooring, carpet and a breaker box.  There is an abundance of character and built-ins throughout the entire house including a fireplace in the living room surrounded with shelving and cabinets along with a huge family room in the basement.
